snippet.title: Official Announcement | Gearbox and Rogue Snail are Working Together on Relic Hunters Legend!
snippet.description:
Rogue Snail and Gearbox Publishing are proud to announce their partnership in bringing Relic Hunters Legend to life. The upcoming top-down, looter-shooter RPG, is full of shooting, looting, and having fun with friends!

Stay tuned for more exciting news. 

#Gearbox #RelicHuntersLegend #RelicHunters #GamingDev #Gaming #Games #Indiegaming #Shooterlooter #RPG
